h3cDvpn.name: h3cDvpn
h3cDvpn.contactinfo: Platform Team Huawei 3Com Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:100085
h3cDvpn.description: This MIB is Dynamic Virtual Private Network(Dvpn) mib. This MIB is applicable to router. Some objects in this may be used only for some specific products, so users should refer to the related documents to acquire more detail information.

DvpnAlgorithmSuite.name: DvpnAlgorithmSuite
DvpnAlgorithmSuite.description: 13 kinds of dvpn algorithms. encryption method | hash method | key width. dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: des | md5 | 768 dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: des | md5 | 1024 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: des | sha1 | 768 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: des | sha1 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: 3des | md5 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: 3des | md5 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: 3des | sha1 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: 3des | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: Aes | md5 | 768 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: Aes | md5 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp768: Aes | sha1 | 768 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp1024: Aes | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAlgorithmNone: none | none | no key

DvpnCommunicateType.name: DvpnCommunicateType
DvpnCommunicateType.description: The type of the communication between client and server. It indicates the direction of the communication.

h3cDvpnServiceEnable.name: h3cDvpnServiceEnable
h3cDvpnServiceEnable.description: Dvpn service enable or disable. If dvpn service is 'disable', dvpn service can not be used.

h3cDvpnClassNumber.name: h3cDvpnClassNumber
h3cDvpnClassNumber.description: The number of dvpn classes. It is only used on client.

h3cDvpnClientNumber.name: h3cDvpnClientNumber
h3cDvpnClientNumber.description: The number of clients which register on the server. When a session of server to client type is built, add 1 to the value of this node. It is only used on server.

h3cDvpnMapAgeTime.name: h3cDvpnMapAgeTime
h3cDvpnMapAgeTime.description: Dvpn map age time, the unit is second. It is only used on server.

h3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval.name: h3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval
h3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval.description: The length of time between the registering of client, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

h3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb.name: h3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb
h3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb.description: The length of time when client dumbs, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

h3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry.name: h3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry
h3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry.description: Regist retry times of client after register fail. It is only used on client.

h3cDvpnDropPkt.name: h3cDvpnDropPkt
h3cDvpnDropPkt.description: The number of packets have been droped.

h3cDvpnOutputPkt.name: h3cDvpnOutputPkt
h3cDvpnOutputPkt.description: The number of packets have been sent.

h3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt.name: h3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt
h3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets.

h3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.name: h3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt
h3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of packets have been encrypted wrongly.

h3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.name: h3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole
h3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.description: The current role of the device. The value is decided by the configuration of the tunnel-interface.

h3cDvpnSessionNumber.name: h3cDvpnSessionNumber
h3cDvpnSessionNumber.description: The number of dvpn sessiones including the session of all states.

h3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey.name: h3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey
h3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey.description: The pre-shared-key of server. It is only used on server.

h3cDvpnMapTrapEnable.name: h3cDvpnMapTrapEnable
h3cDvpnMapTrapEnable.description: Dvpn map trap enable or disable.

h3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable.name: h3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable
h3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable.description: Dvpn session trap enable or disable.

h3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection.name: h3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection
h3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection.description: Clear all dvpn conects in the domain, the parameter is the id of the domain.

h3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.name: h3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo
h3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.description: Clear the statistic information of dvpn.

h3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.name: h3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber
h3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.description: The number of redirect packets. It is only used on server.

h3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.name: h3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType
h3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.description: Dvpn global authentication type being used by server to client. The value is decided by the configuration by the user.

h3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.name: h3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain
h3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn global AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which is used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

h3cDvpnLocalDeviceId.name: h3cDvpnLocalDeviceId
h3cDvpnLocalDeviceId.description: The device ID, it is a string.

h3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime
h3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.description: The age-time of the h3cDvpnSessionHisTable table. The unit is hour.

h3cDvpnSessionHisReset.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisReset
h3cDvpnSessionHisReset.description: The reset flag of dvpn h3cDvpnSessionHisTable table.

h3cDvpnPolicyTable.name: h3cDvpnPolicyTable
h3cDvpnPolicyTable.description: The dvpn policy table. It is used on dvpn server.

h3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType.name: h3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType
h3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType.description: The authentication type used by server to client. The value is decided by the policy configuration of the user. The default value is none.

h3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.name: h3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite
h3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used when session is created.

h3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.name: h3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime
h3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.description: The session idle time, the unit is second.

h3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.name: h3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime
h3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.description: The session keepalive time, the unit is second.

h3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.name: h3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval
h3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.description: The session setup interval time, the unit is second.

h3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.name: h3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite
h3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the session for createing ipsec sa.

h3cDvpnPoSaSeconds.name: h3cDvpnPoSaSeconds
h3cDvpnPoSaSeconds.description: The duration of DVPN IPSec security association. The unit is second.

h3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.name: h3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain
h3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn policy AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

h3cDvpnPoRefTimes.name: h3cDvpnPoRefTimes
h3cDvpnPoRefTimes.description: The total times of the policy being used by dvpn.

h3cDvpnPoRowStatus.name: h3cDvpnPoRowStatus
h3cDvpnPoRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. We support the characteristic of active(1),createAndGo(4),destroy(6).

h3cDvpnDomainSessionNum.name: h3cDvpnDomainSessionNum
h3cDvpnDomainSessionNum.description: The number of session in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum.name: h3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum
h3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum.description: The number of redirect packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainInputPkt.name: h3cDvpnDomainInputPkt
h3cDvpnDomainInputPkt.description: The number of input packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainDropPkt.name: h3cDvpnDomainDropPkt
h3cDvpnDomainDropPkt.description: The number of drop packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt.name: h3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt
h3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt.description: The number of output packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.name: h3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt
h3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.name: h3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt
h3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of encrypt error packets in this dvpn domain.

h3cDvpnClassTable.name: h3cDvpnClassTable
h3cDvpnClassTable.description: The Dvpn class table. It is only used on dvpn client.

h3cDvpnClassName.name: h3cDvpnClassName
h3cDvpnClassName.description: The dvpn class name. It is the index of h3cDvpnClassTable.

h3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType.name: h3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType
h3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType.description: Dvpn server public ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

h3cDvpnClServerPriIpType.name: h3cDvpnClServerPriIpType
h3cDvpnClServerPriIpType.description: Dvpn server private ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

h3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.name: h3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite
h3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the client when sending registry packets to the server. 'dvpnAlgorithmNone' is not supported here.

h3cDvpnClAuthenServerType.name: h3cDvpnClAuthenServerType
h3cDvpnClAuthenServerType.description: The authentication type being used by client to server. The value is decided by the class configuration of the user. The default value is none.

h3cDvpnClPreShareKey.name: h3cDvpnClPreShareKey
h3cDvpnClPreShareKey.description: Dvpn PreShareKey. It is used when the method used by client when authenticating server is pre-share-key, only when the value of the key is the same as that on the server, the client can authenticate server successfully.

h3cDvpnClUserName.name: h3cDvpnClUserName
h3cDvpnClUserName.description: Dvpn UserName. It is configured by the user.

h3cDvpnClPasswd.name: h3cDvpnClPasswd
h3cDvpnClPasswd.description: Dvpn password. It is configured by the user.

h3cDvpnClassRowStatus.name: h3cDvpnClassRowStatus
h3cDvpnClassRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. Only 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy' are supported.

h3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.name: h3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType
h3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.description: The type of dvpn tunnel (client or server).

h3cDvpnTunnelAcl.name: h3cDvpnTunnelAcl
h3cDvpnTunnelAcl.description: The security acl used by the tunnel. If a packet permits the rules, it will not be encrypted.

h3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType.name: h3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType
h3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType.description: The register type used by the client . Only the interface type is client, it can be used. undistributed: If a client send a packet to the client with this configuration, setver will only forward the packet whitout sending redirect packets. forward: The client with this configuration will only send packets forwarded by server, which means it can not initiate to build a session with other clients. undistributedandforward: The client with this configuration have the characteristics of both 'forward' and 'undistributed'. normal: The client with this configuration can build session with other clients without any restriction.

h3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId.name: h3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId
h3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId.description: The dvpn ID used by the tunnel. The dvpn ID is 0 means that user does not configure dvpn ID. User can not configure a dvpn ID with 0.

h3cDvpnTunnelPolicy.name: h3cDvpnTunnelPolicy
h3cDvpnTunnelPolicy.description: The dvpn policy used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is server, it can be used.

h3cDvpnTunnelClass.name: h3cDvpnTunnelClass
h3cDvpnTunnelClass.description: The dvpn class used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is client, it can be used.

h3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.name: h3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId
h3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

h3cDvpnMapDvpnId.name: h3cDvpnMapDvpnId
h3cDvpnMapDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the map belongs to. The dvpn ID is 0 means that the map has not been built. It has not gotten the dvpn ID at that time.

h3cDvpnMapBuildTime.name: h3cDvpnMapBuildTime
h3cDvpnMapBuildTime.description: The time of the map created, the unit is second.

h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.name: h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType
h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp.name: h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp
h3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of map peer device.

h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.name: h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType
h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.name: h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp
h3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.description: The public ip of map peer device.

h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.name: h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType
h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp.name: h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp
h3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of map local device.

h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.name: h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType
h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.name: h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp
h3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.description: The public ip of map local device.

h3cDvpnMapUserName.name: h3cDvpnMapUserName
h3cDvpnMapUserName.description: The user name used by the client registering to server. If the client is not been authenticated, this is a null string.

h3cDvpnMapUdpPort.name: h3cDvpnMapUdpPort
h3cDvpnMapUdpPort.description: The udp port used by map peer device.

h3cDvpnMapType.name: h3cDvpnMapType
h3cDvpnMapType.description: The type of the map. 'clientToclient' is not supported here.

h3cDvpnMapState.name: h3cDvpnMapState
h3cDvpnMapState.description: mapClientInit: The client initiates the map. mapClientBegin: The client begins the process of registering to the server. mapClientAlgreq: The client requests to negotiate the algorithm. mapClientKexReq: The client requests to negotiate the key. mapClientAuthenReq: The client sends authentication information to the server. mapClientConfigReq: The client requests to get some configuration information from the server. Do not support now. mapClientReq: The client requests to register to the server. mapClientSuccess: The client registers to the server successfully. mapServerBegin: The server begins the process of receive a new register. mapServerAlgorithm:The sever begins to negotiate Algorithm. mapServerKexInit: The server replys to the algorithm negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to negotiate key. mapServerAuthenInit: The server replys to the key negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to authenticate client, in the case of the authentication-client method is not none. mapServerConfigInit: The server send some configuration information to client. Do not support now. mapServerInit: The server replys to the authentication packet from the client successfully and begin to receive client information. mapServerFinished: The server receives client information successfully.

h3cDvpnSessionDvpnId.name: h3cDvpnSessionDvpnId
h3cDvpnSessionDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType
h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIp.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIp
h3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId
h3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.description: The device ID of session peer device. It is a string.

h3cDvpnSessionBuildTime.name: h3cDvpnSessionBuildTime
h3cDvpnSessionBuildTime.description: The time of the Session being built, the unit is second.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType
h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp
h3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.description: The public ip of session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.name: h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType
h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.name: h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp
h3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.description: The public ip of session local device.

h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.name: h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType
h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.name: h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp
h3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of session local device.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort
h3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.description: The udp port used by session peer device .

h3cDvpnSessionUserName.name: h3cDvpnSessionUserName
h3cDvpnSessionUserName.description: The user's name. If the session type is client to client, the value of this object is a null string.

h3cDvpnSessionState.name: h3cDvpnSessionState
h3cDvpnSessionState.description: The state of the session. sessionSetupInit: The initiation of the session. sessionSetupReq: The initiator requests to negotiate the SA and so on of the session. sessionSetupSuccess: The session has been built successfully. sessionRekeyReq: The initiator requests to renegotiate the SA. sessionRekeyRep: The passive side replies with a SA renegotiation response packet successfully.

h3cDvpnSessionPeerType.name: h3cDvpnSessionPeerType
h3cDvpnSessionPeerType.description: The type of the session peer device. It may be client software or a router.

h3cDvpnSessionHisTable.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisTable
h3cDvpnSessionHisTable.description: The dvpn session history table. This table contains session's history information, include input/output packet number, up/down time, etc. This table will exist during the 'h3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime'.

h3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID
h3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType
h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP
h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

h3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt
h3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.description: The number of sent packets on the session.

h3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt
h3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.description: The number of received packets on the session.

h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber
h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.description: The number of the session online.

h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag
h3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.description: If the session is online, the value is 'yes'. If the session is not online, the value is 'no'.

h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.name: h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId
h3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

h3cDvpnMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the DVPN MIB.
